com.wookler.server.common.structs

Class ConcurrentCircularList<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.wookler.server.common.structs.ConcurrentCircularList<T>
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    StaticCircularList

    public class ConcurrentCircularList<T>
extends Object
    Basic implementation of a circular linked list. This is a concurrent implementation and hence thread safe.
    Author:
    Subho Ghosh (subho dot ghosh at outlook.com)
